{"tid":1114973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心偷食蘇州屎】樂大媽鬧爆幾粒鐘 黃心穎拍旅遊特輯隨時要搵人補拍","createTime":"2019-04-18T21:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:39:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17082e6bc992fa150a320de468bb68caa69fe592","tid":1114973,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T21:48:40.000Z","msg":"安心偷食嘅女主主黃心穎，噚日終於係IG蒲頭，用一百六十五個字回應「我做錯了」。據了解報導出街後，無綫高層樂易玲主動接洽黃心穎，兩人傾電話長達幾個鐘，全程怒片訓話。又難怪樂大媽火燒心，辛辛苦苦力捧，開始有能力幫公司賺錢之際，竟然送自己一份大禮，自斷米路，唔怒就勢係假，最慘就係有大堆「蘇州史」要執手尾，先平息網民的怒火，刪走佢主唱嘅《開心速遞》主題曲，跟手將佢兩套主演嘅劇集《堅離地愛堅離地》同埋《牛下女高音》抽起，而早前為馬來西亞旅遊局拍落嘅旅遊特輯，要刪走黃心穎的部分自然在所難免，但有關方面分分鐘要求大台派人補拍，介時呢筆額外費用由大台負責，定係要當事人「自己的事自己處理」呢，認真拭目以待！<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190418/large/1555580834_95cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190418%2Flarge%2F1555580834_95cc.jpg&h=cbea2775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_665378_0?obdraft=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_665378_0%3Fobdraft%3Dtrue&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=360a57cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_665378_0%3Fobdraft%3Dtrue&h=ce84e4dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_665378_0?obdraft=true</a>"},{"pid":"86f338a42cba0b68ff90b934c3ae3d0d11f31b9b","tid":1114973,"uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T21:57:00.000Z","msg":"永不錄用啦"},{"pid":"e8bf1526635d700a165f5eb08db86a816318d6c0","tid":1114973,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T22:11:38.000Z","msg":"吓，有邊個唔知620最想要嘅係收視，不過今舖蘋果攞咗第一啫"},{"pid":"7ba083a99c6e4dcf68e4b44fe638e4082982f70d","tid":1114973,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T22:17:43.000Z","msg":"請馬明補拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/k